(2, 'About US', 'about-us', '', '<div class="content">\r\n<p><strong>WASS</strong> is an India based professional Web Development, Windows Development, Products and Multimedia. Company provides affordable and personalized Web Designing, Web Application Development, Desktop application Development, ERP Application Development, Flash Animation, 3D Animation, Graphic Designing, Broacher/Catalogue Designing, Web Promotion, and Multimedia Presentations, Data conversion and also offers BPO Services. We target to create visually appealing, easy-to-navigate Website design keeping in mind the target audience. We are committed to deliver work in time with the maximum possible quality. It is the basis of our organization. The yardstick of our success is customer satisfaction.<br /> Our attitude towards clients being friendly and flexible in nature, which in turns helps to ensures long-term partnerships with our clients. We deal everything with excellent professionalism with full return on investment.</p>\r\n<p>We provide to our clients - Best quality, efficient, eye-catching and cost effective website designing, web application development, Desktop Application Development and Multimedia Application.</p>\r\n<p>We withstand better than others due to the highly qualified and creative team of professionals.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Introduction</strong></p>\r\n<p>we provide the below mentioned services to our valuable clients under one shed. We always worked to the smiles of our clients and the jingles of their pockets because we value their satisfaction and appreciation more than any other statistics.</p>\r\n<p><strong>We offer following services.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Website Designing / Redesigning,<br /> Website Development,<br /> Windows Application,<br /> 2D &amp; 3D Animation,<br /> Broacher / Catalogue designing,<br /> Multimedia Presentations,<br /> Logo Designing,<br /> Graphic Designing,</p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2011-06-16 15:32:23', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '