(3, 'Services', 'services', '', '<div class="inner">\r\n<div class="node">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<p><strong>Services</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="menu">\r\n<li>Web  Development</li>\r\n<li>Desktop  Development</li>\r\n<li>Products</li>\r\n<li>Web  Designing</li>\r\n<li>2D  &amp; 3D Animation</li>\r\n<li>E-Learning</li>\r\n<li>Logo  Designing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong><strong>E-Commerce</strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>A lot of  importance is attached to e-commerce as a vehicle to carry out online  transactions.</p>\r\n<p>Needless to say, it has  fast evolved as an industry. Customized e-commerce solutions have helped  companies carry out transactions 24x7. Compared to the benefits the solution is  economical. An e-commerce solution customized to your needs can help you  harness the full potential of the internet.</p>\r\n<p>WASS is an e-commerce solutions providing company servicing  clients across the globe.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Our e-commerce solutions include:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="menu">\r\n<li>Payment gateway solution </li>\r\n<li>Shopping cart integration </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Our solution includes:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="menu">\r\n<li>Development of sites       empowered by different kinds of shopping carts customized to your needs. </li>\r\n<li>Providing payment gateways       solution through secured servers. </li>\r\n<li>Integration of payment       gateways to websites that already have accounts with gateway service       providers. </li>\r\n<li>Optimization of the site for       the service provider''s system. </li>\r\n<li>Development, maintenance and       hosting customized e-commerce solutions such as e-mails, database       information, etc. for corporate clients. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Payment  Gateway </strong></p>\r\n<p>Engineers  at WASS can set up payment gateway shopping carts to assist credit card  processing online. They are experienced in setting up payment gateways with a  wide variety of service providers. With the support of the solution developed  by us you can put an end to long wait for checks. Our e-commerce payment  gateway solution enables you to:</p>\r\n<p><strong>It enables you:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="menu">\r\n<li>Sell products through built-in shopping carts. </li>\r\n<li>Accept credit cards online. </li>\r\n<li>Easy integration. You just have to place link on your       site. </li>\r\n<li>Management from web based control panel. </li>\r\n<li>Verisign security. </li>\r\n<li>Order notification by e-mail. </li>\r\n<li>Secure transactions with Verisign SSL connections. </li>\r\n<li>Immediate authorization. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Shopping Cart  Integration </strong></p>\r\n<p>An  integrated shopping cart is an effective means of doing business online. It is  fast, reliable and easy as it enables your customers to buy from you over the  internet. As part of its e-commerce solutions WASS offers shopping cart  integration as well. We develop your customized shopping cart enabling your  business to go online.</p>\r\n<p><strong>We do:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="menu">\r\n<li>Specialized work in designing and hosting e-commerce       enabled sites. </li>\r\n<li>Shopping cart development with various options such       as standard shopping cart, customized shopping cart and payment gateway       integrated shopping cart. </li>\r\n<li>Integration of the website solution with the service       provider''s system. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2011-06-16 15:34:16', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-16 15:34:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 4, '', '', 0, 23, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(4, 'Solutions', 'solutions', '', '<div class="node">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<p><strong>Web Solutions</strong></p>\r\n<p>Clients  don''t want websites; they want their identity or business from their websites.  And this understanding is our guiding light in providing web solutions. Take a  look at our entire service range for web.</p>\r\n<p>Our  range of web solutions has been designed so as to provide you with all round  support. Our web solutions do not end at merely making an eye catching website  but it aims at communicating the right message to the right kind of audience.  Web: today a meeting place for each and every person tomorrow will surely take  the form of an identity source for each and every individual on the globe. So  keeping an entity alive amongst such tough competition and making sure that it  is the best in itself, needs much more than mere technical skills. So  integrating different aspects of Web, we create web based solutions for our  esteemed clients.</p>\r\n<p>A website is no more a matter of fancy. It has soon evolved into a business  requirement with its vast revenue generating and communication facilities.  Consumers have got hooked on to the web. Provided that these advances are  exploited in the right way, a business establishment can add to its prospects.  Keeping with our aim to use these opportunities in an efficient way, we provide  the following services.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Web designing </strong></p>\r\n<p>Every firm or institution has a different style of functioning and a different  set of aims. We will design your site in such a way that it reflects the spirit  of your organization. We will use your inputs and our expertise in such a way  that it turns out to be the best possible option for you.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Portal Development </strong><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>Portal development  is a combination of expertise at different tasks. That makes the task all the  more cumbersome. And we have the judicious blend of expertise and experience  with us that will help us serve you in an efficient manner and build the portal  of your dreams. In the past, we have developed portals with our task beginning  from planning and ending only after the successful approval of the client.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Promotion of web  site </strong></p>\r\n<p>The best of the websites fail to create the desired impact for the sole reason  that it fails to attract the required attention. We promote your website in  such a way that it gets submitted in the leading search engines of the world.  To put it simply, we help you get noticed.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Revamping of  existing web sites </strong></p>\r\n<p>If you have a  website that is just not good enough, don''t fret. We will take a look at your  website, suggest modifications, refurbish the entire website and model it  according to your tastes.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Backend Database  Processing </strong></p>\r\n<p>Keeping in view your distinct requirements, we will link your website to  backend database. This includes links to SQL Server, Oracle, MS-Access and My  SQL.</p>\r\n<p><strong>E-commerce B2B and  B2C services </strong></p>\r\n<p>If putting  your B2B and B2C plans into implementation is proving difficult, we can help  you. We will build you a B2B site that will be in tandem with your company''s  e-commerce strategies. It will ease your business dealings over the internet.  The B2C sites built by us will help you get in touch with your customers and  further your business prospects. Our job is not over after the physical  building of the site. We even give valuable guidance for you to build up your  business over the net.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Multimedia Solutions</strong></p>\r\n<p>Multimedia Design ensures maximum penetration with higher acceptance levels,  when it comes to communicating your message, professionally produced multimedia  presentation on CD, DVD or via the internet excite your customers senses and  engage them in an interactive experience as they are taken on a guided tour of  your products and services.</p>\r\n<p>Our areas of expertise are in creating Multimedia CD-Rom based learning  programs, corporate multimedia presentations, online multimedia games,  scientific and biomedical multimedia animations, multimedia web design, or  multimedia video web, we can create anything your mind can imagine.</p>\r\n<p>We also provide multimedia-programming service, including database-driven  applications to help make your site more dynamic and to meet your business needs.  Our multimedia experts give you a unique multimedia solution; by providing  customized software according to your multimedia requirement. Our multimedia  solutions include Graphic Design and 3D Development. As stated above we can  even put your Multimedia Design for the World Wide Web.</p>\r\n<p>WASS provides Multimedia Outsourcing Solution Services and  Offshore Multimedia Development Service from India<br /> <strong><br /> </strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2011-06-16 15:34:36', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-16 15:34:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 12, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(5, 'Portfolio', 'portfolio', '', '<div class="node">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<p>Every company or individual have different needs, and we can fulfill all of them. We will not try to persuade you, but we will advise you. We create custom websites, flash intros, presentations, games, brochures.</p>\r\n<p>Every piece we have ever been hired for was created with thoughtfulness and care, keeping the client''s individual wants and needs in mind.</p>\r\n<p>Browse our portfolio to see some of our work. Whether you need a complete website, with all the gadgets, or just a Flash intro, presentation, logo or a banner, we are the right choice. Contact us and let us know what you need!</p>\r\n<table border="0" width="100%">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.happynetworkfamily.com" target="_blank"><img src="sites/default/files/happyway.jpg" border="0" /></a><a href="http://www.lookdiscounts.com/"><img src="sites/default/files/look.jpg" border="0" /></a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2011-06-16 15:37:38', 62, '', '2011-06-17 07:34:13', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-16 15:37:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 15, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(6, 'Web Design', 'web-design', '', '<div class="content">\r\n<p><strong>Logo Design </strong> <br /> <br /> Ever wondered what your  company logo means to your customers? <br /> <br /> It  is part of your business identity. An impressive and eye-catching logo goes a  long way in furthering your business goals. It is the first thing people look  at and it is your first opportunity to make a positive impression on your  customers. As a visual identity of your company, the logo helps to create brand  recognition. A good logo and high quality corporate identity are the ways to make  an immediate impact. You will never have to introduce yourself twice! A quality  logo can instantly and intuitively communicate style, professionalism, overall  presence and even the philosophy of a business. Simple, but not so easy! <br /> <br /> We  offer custom logo designing as part of its creative designing services. We  service clients from all over the world. When there are so many logo design  companies, why us? WASS is a company with a global reach. From  us you get a powerful eye-catching logo that will enable you to carve out your  distinctive identity. We can give you the professional image you are looking  for.</p>\r\n<p><br /> <br /> <strong>We give you:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="menu">\r\n<li>Uncompromising services. </li>\r\n<li>Unparalleled quality. </li>\r\n<li>Unforgettable results. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>No matter what your needs  are-new company logo design or a change of corporate image-we design it for  you. Our skilled designers put their experience, knowledge and talent into your  project. What you get is a unique logo that is aesthetically designed and helps  to create an impression. A logo designed by us will set you apart from other  companies in your industry and your competitors. You know all about your  business and we know all about custom logo designing. Let this professional  collaboration spell success for you. All our clients are winners. To know more  about our work views our updated portfolio. <br /> <br /> We specialize in custom  logo designing and endeavor to meet our customer''s requirements.</p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2011-06-16 15:39:27', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-16 15:39:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 0, 'robots=\nauthor=');

